{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4764392fa3","title":"关于打招呼会议的两个批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0dab767b3b","index":0,"year":1975,"month":11,"day":22,"articleId":"4764392fa3","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"批邓反击右倾翻案风","id":"b88b47c25d","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7424da5653","type":"title","text":"关于打招呼会议的两个批语","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4764392fa3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"331e16b54a","type":"paragraph","text":"很好。但不仅只是老同志，要有中年、青年各一人同听同议，如同此次十七人会议那样。即也要对青年人打招呼，否则青年人也会犯错误。请政治局再议一次，或者分两次开，或者先分后合。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4764392fa3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5007e6019c","type":"paragraph","text":"小平同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4764392fa3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fc4f95b7ae","type":"paragraph","text":"还是你们议的好，先给老同志打招呼。青年问题暂缓。因有的还未结合，有的在打派仗（如七机部），有的貌合神离（如清华），召集不起来。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4764392fa3","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}